nd|first3=E. A.|title='Women Do Not Count, Neither Shall They Be Counted': Suffrage, Citizenship and the Battle for the 1911 Census|journal=History Workshop Journal|date=Spring 2011|issue=17|pages=98\u2013127|issn=4130-6813|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite news|last1=Marsh|first1=Joanna|title=Warrior woman: my cantata for suffragette Emily Davison|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2018/jan/31/cantata-suffragette-emily-davison-joanna-marsh|accessdate=3 February 2018|work=The Guardian|date=31 January 2018|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web|title=Mayor Marks Centenary of Women's Suffrage|url=https://www.london.gov.uk/press-releases/mayoral/mayor-marks-centenary-of-womens-suffrage|publisher=Mayor of London|date=6 February 2018|accessdate=26 April 2018|ref={{sfnRef|\"Mayor Marks Centenary of Women's Suffrage\", Mayor of London}}}}\n* {{cite news|title=Miss Davison's Death: Inquest and Verdict|work=The Manchester Guardian|date=11 June 1913|page=9|ref={{sfnRef|\"Miss Davison's Death\", ''The Manchester Guardian''}}}}\n* {{cite news|title=Miss Davison's Funeral: Impressive London Procession|work=The Manchester Guardian|date=16 June 1913|page=9|ref={{sfnRef|\"Miss Davison's Funeral\", ''The Manchester Guardian''}}}}\n* {{cite news|title=Miss Davison's Funeral|work=Votes for Women|date=20 June 1913|page=553|ref={{sfnRef|\"Miss Davison's Funeral\", ''Votes for Women''}}}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Morley|first1=Ann|last2=Stanley|first2=Liz|title=The Life and Death of Emily Wilding Davison|date=1988|publisher=The Women's Press|location=London|isbn=978-0-7043-4133-3|ref=harv}}\n* {{Cite journal|last=Naylor|first=Fay|year=2011|title=Emily Wilding Davison: Martyr or Firebrand?|url=https://www.royalholloway.ac.uk/alumni/documents/pdf/higher/higher15.pdf|journal=Higher Magazine|access-date=27 June 2017|publisher=Royal Holloway, University of London|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite news|title=A Night in Guy Fawkes Cupboard|work=Votes For Women|date=7 April 1911|page=441|ref={{sfnRef|\"A Night in Guy Fawkes Cupboard\",